WEBVTT

00:12.090 --> 00:16.140
[2012]

00:34.640 --> 00:35.640
Is this your girl?

00:48.670 --> 00:49.670
Give it back to me!

00:50.030 --> 00:51.200
Give it back to me!

01:03.670 --> 01:05.330
Everyone, search carefully.

01:05.349 --> 01:06.870
There should be a pocket watch.

01:06.870 --> 01:07.950
Yes!

01:38.070 --> 01:40.229
Protect Zhou Jin.

01:40.840 --> 01:42.350
I must protect Zhou Jin.

01:44.430 --> 01:45.430
I promise you.

01:45.680 --> 01:47.229
I promise you, okay?

03:10.580 --> 03:16.190
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:16.440 --> 03:18.810
[Episode 23]

03:33.190 --> 03:34.240
Command vehicle!

03:35.710 --> 03:37.400
Junior, we need firefighter backup.

03:37.400 --> 03:39.190
You can't go there! It's dangerous!

03:39.190 --> 03:39.840
Zhou!

03:39.840 --> 03:41.310
Hansheng!

03:41.870 --> 03:43.470
Calm down, Junior.

03:44.190 --> 03:45.850
You can't go over there, Zhou!

03:46.700 --> 03:47.280
Zhou!

03:47.280 --> 03:47.880
Hansheng!

03:47.970 --> 03:48.690
Zhou!

03:50.120 --> 03:51.470
Hansheng!

03:52.060 --> 03:53.990
Calm down, Junior!

03:55.079 --> 03:56.000
Hansheng!

03:56.020 --> 03:56.710
Zhou!

03:57.120 --> 03:58.079
Hansheng!

03:58.680 --> 04:00.430
Calm down, Junior!

04:00.590 --> 04:01.360
You can't go over there!

04:01.360 --> 04:02.080
Hansheng!

04:02.360 --> 04:03.520
Zhou Jin, stay calm!

04:03.520 --> 04:04.120
Hansheng!

04:04.310 --> 04:04.870
Junior!

04:04.870 --> 04:05.680
Hansheng!

04:05.700 --> 04:06.980
Junior, calm down!

04:07.750 --> 04:08.400
Zhou Jin!

05:30.630 --> 05:31.830
Why didn't you knock?

05:33.500 --> 05:34.830
The door wasn't locked.

05:36.920 --> 05:39.050
Hospital room doors don't have locks.

05:47.040 --> 05:48.370
Are you feeling better?

05:49.870 --> 05:50.510
I'm okay.

05:53.750 --> 05:55.150
What exactly do you mean?

06:01.750 --> 06:02.390
Zhou Jin.

06:04.870 --> 06:06.930
Let's keep some distance between us.

06:16.600 --> 06:18.130
So you still want a divorce.

06:19.830 --> 06:20.960
What's your reason?

06:30.270 --> 06:32.130
If it's because of Jiang Cheng...

06:32.820 --> 06:33.750
Jiang Hansheng,

06:35.480 --> 06:36.430
you know me.

06:38.190 --> 06:39.450
Whether it's marriage

06:39.630 --> 06:40.800
or love,

06:41.720 --> 06:43.240
I'm not a casual person.

06:54.830 --> 06:55.890
So here's the deal.

06:56.430 --> 06:57.600
If you say

06:57.950 --> 06:59.120
that you hate me,

06:59.950 --> 07:02.040
I'll sign the divorce papers right away.

07:02.040 --> 07:03.830
You can keep your car and house,

07:03.830 --> 07:05.560
and we'll go our separate ways.

07:20.300 --> 07:21.010
Do you really

07:21.010 --> 07:22.810
have no feelings for me anymore?

07:26.190 --> 07:27.360
Do you dare to say it?

07:34.720 --> 07:35.270
Zhou Jin.

07:37.240 --> 07:38.500
You don't understand.

07:39.950 --> 07:41.480
I really don't understand.

07:41.510 --> 07:43.440
If you tell me, won't I understand?

07:48.480 --> 07:50.480
You should have the right to choose.

07:52.480 --> 07:54.610
Jiang Cheng was in prison at that time.

07:54.950 --> 07:57.080
He couldn't tell you what he was doing.

07:57.920 --> 07:59.580
He could only let you hate him.

08:00.240 --> 08:01.240
You had no choice.

08:02.270 --> 08:04.270
When I was helping you with the case,

08:05.000 --> 08:06.000
I never asked you

08:06.680 --> 08:08.810
if you actually needed my help either.

08:09.750 --> 08:10.800
I was too selfish.

08:12.120 --> 08:14.190
I forced my way into your life.

08:15.680 --> 08:17.480
That's not fair to you, Zhou Jin.

08:18.630 --> 08:20.690
You should have the chance to choose,

08:21.430 --> 08:22.870
knowing all the facts.

08:26.430 --> 08:28.040
I already know everything.

08:29.950 --> 08:32.080
I still don't want to change anything.

08:35.150 --> 08:37.549
There are still many things
you don't know.

08:38.510 --> 08:39.150
Zhou Jin.

08:40.840 --> 08:42.570
You don't really know me at all.

08:43.440 --> 08:44.770
Haven't you been asking

08:45.440 --> 08:47.000
why I can always find you?

08:52.670 --> 08:54.530
Because I've been following you.

08:56.390 --> 08:57.790
Ma'am, give me a steamed bun.

08:57.790 --> 08:58.670
Okay.

09:01.100 --> 09:02.550
How about a tea egg too?

09:02.570 --> 09:02.930
Sure.

09:04.870 --> 09:05.750
Five years ago,

09:06.460 --> 09:08.220
when we went to arrest Qi Yan,

09:09.510 --> 09:11.200
he stole my pocket watch.

09:12.270 --> 09:13.360
Inside the watch

09:13.510 --> 09:14.550
was your photo.

09:16.230 --> 09:18.320
Those people have seen what you look like.

09:18.320 --> 09:20.550
Although I always thought Qi Yan was dead,

09:20.550 --> 09:22.030
I still felt uneasy.

09:22.670 --> 09:24.330
I was afraid that someone else

09:24.510 --> 09:25.440
might try to get revenge on me

09:25.440 --> 09:26.320
by finding you

09:27.150 --> 09:29.140
and doing something crazy to you.

09:41.120 --> 09:44.740
♪ I should never have let you bear this ♪

09:48.400 --> 09:52.490
♪ I always want to give you
everything I have ♪

09:55.790 --> 09:59.740
♪ If only it could win your heart,
even for a moment ♪

10:00.150 --> 10:03.490
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

10:05.030 --> 10:07.310
♪ They're so free ♪

10:10.680 --> 10:14.800
♪ I never want to see you hang your head ♪

10:17.970 --> 10:21.040
♪ I keep dreaming of
what lies ahead for us ♪

10:25.310 --> 10:29.250
♪ If only it could keep us
in love forever ♪

10:29.780 --> 10:33.010
♪ Look at the zebras ♪

10:33.640 --> 10:36.300
♪ How freely they swim ♪

10:38.210 --> 10:41.280
♪ How can I tell you ♪

10:41.310 --> 10:44.940
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

10:45.610 --> 10:48.430
♪ I am sure to ♪

10:48.460 --> 10:52.010
♪ Walk with you ♪

10:53.040 --> 10:56.510
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

10:56.530 --> 11:00.660
♪ One more glance is not enough ♪

11:00.680 --> 11:02.900
♪ At the crossroad ♪

11:02.930 --> 11:06.300
♪ To the left or right ♪

11:07.300 --> 11:11.220
♪ I want to hold your hand ♪

11:15.790 --> 11:17.320
Qi Yan used me

11:17.960 --> 11:18.900
to threaten you,

11:19.870 --> 11:21.320
so for these three years,

11:23.120 --> 11:24.780
you've always been by my side?

11:29.200 --> 11:31.080
If I couldn't see that you were safe,

11:31.080 --> 11:33.210
my heart would be in constant anxiety,

11:33.510 --> 11:35.710
and I wouldn't be able to live normally.

11:38.440 --> 11:40.440
Later when the pocket watch disappeared,

11:40.440 --> 11:42.440
you were afraid I might be in danger,

11:42.720 --> 11:43.920
so you came to Haizhou

11:45.360 --> 11:46.630
to keep protecting me?

11:47.890 --> 11:48.550
That pocket watch

11:48.550 --> 11:50.610
belonged to your brother Zhou Chuan.

12:00.840 --> 12:01.600
I remember.

12:03.120 --> 12:04.080
My brother won it

12:05.910 --> 12:08.510
as a prize in a sniper competition.

12:13.120 --> 12:14.580
Your brother gave it to me.

12:17.270 --> 12:18.530
I really treasured it.

12:21.480 --> 12:23.030
I asked my brother for it before.

12:23.030 --> 12:24.430
He wouldn't give it to me.

12:25.910 --> 12:27.600
He told me mysteriously

12:28.870 --> 12:30.070
that he gave the watch

12:30.720 --> 12:31.750
to someone

12:31.960 --> 12:33.560
who needed it more than I did.

12:37.270 --> 12:38.080
It was you?

12:40.720 --> 12:41.360
Yes.

12:55.270 --> 12:57.000
How can someone like you exist?

12:58.080 --> 12:59.010
Jiang Hansheng.

13:00.720 --> 13:01.480
I'm sorry.

13:03.480 --> 13:04.240
"I'm sorry."

13:06.390 --> 13:08.250
You're always apologizing to me.

13:15.440 --> 13:17.040
I loved you too obsessively.

13:19.030 --> 13:21.490
Obsessive to the point
of being despicable.

13:21.600 --> 13:22.630
At first,

13:23.320 --> 13:24.550
I just wanted to watch you from afar

13:24.550 --> 13:25.950
and that would be enough.

13:27.120 --> 13:28.360
But as time went on,

13:29.630 --> 13:31.230
I wanted you to notice me too.

13:33.480 --> 13:34.880
And once I had the chance,

13:35.530 --> 13:37.130
I even hoped I could have you.

13:38.790 --> 13:40.190
Zhou Jin, I was so afraid.

13:42.280 --> 13:44.540
I was terrified you'd see my selfish side

13:45.240 --> 13:46.520
and start to hate me.

13:48.390 --> 13:50.320
I know I shouldn't get close to you.

13:50.960 --> 13:53.420
Being close to you
would only bring you pain.

13:56.240 --> 13:56.960
I'm sorry.

14:11.550 --> 14:12.480
Then from now on,

14:14.720 --> 14:15.960
stop loving me.

14:23.270 --> 14:23.750
Okay.

14:35.220 --> 14:36.150
Jiang Hansheng,

14:40.200 --> 14:41.930
how can someone like you exist?

14:43.630 --> 14:44.440
From now on,

14:45.200 --> 14:47.060
you don't need to love me anymore.

14:48.800 --> 14:50.130
Let me love you instead.

14:53.210 --> 14:54.480
I will always love you.

14:56.630 --> 14:57.890
I'll love you until...

14:59.000 --> 15:00.870
you stop hating yourself.

15:02.510 --> 15:03.240
Okay?

15:07.720 --> 15:08.360
Zhou Jin.

15:14.790 --> 15:16.120
Let's not get divorced.

15:17.390 --> 15:18.150
Okay?

15:19.870 --> 15:20.510
Zhou Jin.

15:23.150 --> 15:25.480
I might not be able to
take good care of you.

15:25.510 --> 15:28.110
I haven't taken good care
of you before either.

15:29.360 --> 15:30.320
From now on,

15:31.960 --> 15:33.620
we'll take care of each other.

15:34.510 --> 15:35.710
We'll grow together.

15:36.910 --> 15:37.600
Okay?

15:40.870 --> 15:42.590
I want to be good to you.

15:45.840 --> 15:47.370
I want to love you properly.

15:49.370 --> 15:50.650
If you want the moon,

15:51.120 --> 15:53.320
I'll never settle for giving you stars.

15:55.120 --> 15:55.870
Is that okay?

16:05.440 --> 16:06.550
If you don't agree,

16:07.960 --> 16:09.760
I have other ways to win you over.

16:10.200 --> 16:11.730
I'm quite good at it anyway.

16:12.960 --> 16:14.160
Why are you good at it?

16:14.790 --> 16:16.050
What are you thinking?

16:16.510 --> 16:18.240
It's not what you're thinking.

16:22.600 --> 16:23.730
Then I'll have to use

16:24.030 --> 16:25.830
my special tactics just for you.

16:27.770 --> 16:29.770
Don't think I don't understand you.

16:47.790 --> 16:48.720
Jiang Hansheng.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.480
You're blushing.

16:54.790 --> 16:56.450
Is it okay for me to win you over

16:57.150 --> 16:57.790
like this?

17:01.200 --> 17:02.730
Do you still want a divorce?

17:04.550 --> 17:05.079
Zhou Jin.

17:06.680 --> 17:07.349
I love you.

17:14.410 --> 17:15.329
Zhou!

17:15.359 --> 17:17.069
Is this the right room?

17:17.310 --> 17:18.270
It should be.

17:18.910 --> 17:19.950
Let's go in.

17:23.829 --> 17:24.510
How are you?

17:25.270 --> 17:26.200
Feeling better?

17:27.339 --> 17:28.099
Zhou Jin.

17:28.200 --> 17:29.330
whose hospital bed is this?

17:29.330 --> 17:31.720
Get down. So inappropriate.

17:32.470 --> 17:33.200
Take it easy.

17:36.130 --> 17:36.570
Dad.

17:39.360 --> 17:40.710
You look much better.

17:41.240 --> 17:42.640
You're recovering well.

17:42.640 --> 17:43.480
Are you feeling better?

17:43.480 --> 17:43.960
Not bad.

17:45.060 --> 17:46.020
In the future,

17:46.140 --> 17:48.010
don't indulge Zhou Jin.

17:48.310 --> 17:49.510
With her personality,

17:49.510 --> 17:51.170
she easily gets into trouble.

17:52.440 --> 17:53.700
I'm talking about you.

17:53.790 --> 17:54.850
Who do you think you are?

17:54.850 --> 17:56.850
How dare you jump out of a moving car?

17:57.150 --> 17:58.480
Do you have a death wish?

17:59.110 --> 17:59.550
Dad,

17:59.840 --> 18:01.310
this isn't Zhou Jin's fault.

18:01.310 --> 18:02.110
It's my fault.

18:02.310 --> 18:03.440
I couldn't stop her.

18:03.580 --> 18:04.690
I'm scolding her,

18:04.710 --> 18:06.510
and you're still defending her?

18:06.790 --> 18:09.200
I'm not worried about Zhou Jin.
She's full of energy.

18:09.200 --> 18:09.960
But you,

18:10.070 --> 18:11.590
you were seriously injured.

18:11.590 --> 18:12.920
You must rest properly.

18:13.140 --> 18:14.720
It's nothing, Mom. Just a minor injury.

18:14.720 --> 18:15.780
I'll recover soon.

18:16.000 --> 18:17.420
You still need to watch your nutrition.

18:17.420 --> 18:19.350
I'll make some soup for you tonight

18:19.640 --> 18:20.640
and bring it over.

18:21.510 --> 18:22.240
Thanks, Mom.

18:23.030 --> 18:24.070
I want some too.

18:25.250 --> 18:27.250
You want my snakehead fish soup too?

18:28.270 --> 18:28.870
No thanks.

18:31.480 --> 18:32.240
Zhou Jin,

18:32.430 --> 18:33.830
about your work,

18:33.850 --> 18:35.030
I need to say a few more words.

18:35.030 --> 18:36.680
That's enough. Stop lecturing her.

18:36.680 --> 18:37.590
Hey, I'm just concerned about her.

18:37.590 --> 18:38.030
Dad,

18:38.510 --> 18:39.240
don't worry.

18:39.480 --> 18:41.030
I'll look after her from now on.

18:41.030 --> 18:41.590
Good.

18:42.350 --> 18:44.610
Hearing you say that puts my mind at ease.

18:46.440 --> 18:47.550
My dad loves to nag.

18:48.440 --> 18:49.840
He's making my head spin.

19:47.170 --> 19:48.100
You really came.

19:52.130 --> 19:53.510
Are you avoiding Zhou Jin

19:53.510 --> 19:55.000
or her parents?

19:55.310 --> 19:56.240
No.

19:57.420 --> 19:58.680
I just felt suffocated

19:58.960 --> 20:00.560
and came here to get some air.

20:04.800 --> 20:06.060
They've all gone back?

20:09.960 --> 20:12.000
The elderly couple insisted on
coming to the station.

20:12.000 --> 20:14.290
Seems like unless they saw you
with their own eyes,

20:14.290 --> 20:15.690
they wouldn't be at ease.

20:16.590 --> 20:17.960
Their things are at my place,

20:17.960 --> 20:19.420
but they've already left.

20:19.440 --> 20:20.480
I told them

20:20.790 --> 20:21.830
that you're now

20:21.830 --> 20:23.030
a key witness.

20:24.030 --> 20:25.430
You need to be questioned

20:26.160 --> 20:28.070
and also need special protection,

20:28.070 --> 20:29.870
so you're being kept in custody.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.920
Anyway, whatever needs to be discussed

20:31.920 --> 20:33.120
can wait until later.

20:33.270 --> 20:35.200
I won't really be locked up, will I?

20:36.920 --> 20:38.180
Zhou Jin is doing well.

20:38.350 --> 20:39.880
She'll be discharged soon.

20:40.550 --> 20:41.400
I told her

20:42.110 --> 20:44.540
that until the higher-ups
make an official decision,

20:44.540 --> 20:46.140
I'll be responsible for you.

20:46.680 --> 20:48.140
She doesn't need to worry.

20:51.010 --> 20:53.340
There's no trace of Qi Yan
and Qiu Ye at all?

20:57.160 --> 20:58.160
That's exactly

20:59.160 --> 21:00.490
why I needed to find you.

21:01.000 --> 21:02.200
Think carefully.

21:02.790 --> 21:03.920
Is there anyone else

21:05.110 --> 21:06.910
who might know his whereabouts?

21:06.960 --> 21:08.290
Now, Qi is

21:08.880 --> 21:10.680
absolutely determined.

21:11.550 --> 21:13.010
He won't say a single word.

21:15.830 --> 21:17.080
If this continues,

21:18.960 --> 21:20.690
all our efforts will be wasted.

21:21.920 --> 21:23.980
We need to think of another approach.

21:29.070 --> 21:29.960
It's getting late.

21:29.960 --> 21:30.760
Get in the car.

21:30.790 --> 21:32.190
I'll take you home first.

21:42.440 --> 21:44.100
I actually quite like it here.

22:07.350 --> 22:09.080
After Leader Yao's sacrifice,

22:09.310 --> 22:10.840
I know you're feeling down.

22:12.790 --> 22:14.250
I understand how you feel.

22:17.590 --> 22:18.440
Before,

22:20.440 --> 22:22.030
I always met with Yao here.

22:23.350 --> 22:25.610
Sometimes we'd meet down on those rocks,

22:25.640 --> 22:26.510
where it's pitch black,

22:26.510 --> 22:28.110
each of us with a flashlight.

22:28.790 --> 22:31.320
Sometimes we'd just sit
like we were just now.

22:32.110 --> 22:33.070
Once,

22:33.100 --> 22:33.960
during the day,

22:34.750 --> 22:36.680
we pretended to be open-water swimmers

22:36.680 --> 22:38.240
and talked while swimming.

22:40.440 --> 22:41.200
All of this

22:43.160 --> 22:45.020
feels like it was just yesterday.

22:49.510 --> 22:50.110
Chief Tan.

22:51.750 --> 22:53.280
It's been almost six years.

22:53.830 --> 22:55.290
Everything that could be done,

22:55.290 --> 22:56.220
I've done it all.

22:58.830 --> 22:59.640
I believe you.

23:00.960 --> 23:02.030
You did your best.

23:03.000 --> 23:03.480
Yes,

23:04.640 --> 23:05.570
I did try my best.

23:07.000 --> 23:08.240
But Yao is gone.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.330
Zhou Jin is gone too.

23:11.200 --> 23:14.530
The most ridiculous thing
is that even Old Scorpion is gone.

23:15.480 --> 23:16.200
Six years.

23:17.560 --> 23:18.960
I've worked for nothing.

23:19.910 --> 23:21.070
Don't say that.

23:23.590 --> 23:25.720
Actually, we all understand clearly.

23:26.830 --> 23:28.310
The illegal trading chain

23:28.880 --> 23:30.880
that uses Hengyun as its base

23:30.880 --> 23:31.740
of operations,

23:32.000 --> 23:34.050
which is also what Leader Yao called

23:34.300 --> 23:35.300
the Jin-Hai Line,

23:36.030 --> 23:37.690
is gradually becoming clear.

23:38.020 --> 23:40.510
The upstream suppliers
and downstream buyers

23:40.510 --> 23:42.370
have all shown their true colors.

23:42.720 --> 23:44.310
Your contribution was essential.

23:44.310 --> 23:46.370
But Old Scorpion hasn't been caught.

23:46.550 --> 23:48.210
All of this will happen again.

23:48.750 --> 23:50.550
Five years ago, there was the 8/17 Case.

23:50.550 --> 23:51.970
Now there's the Jingang Wharf.

23:51.970 --> 23:53.080
What about next time?

23:53.080 --> 23:54.480
What will it be next time?

23:58.510 --> 23:59.910
Do you have any new ideas?

24:09.590 --> 24:10.260
I'm tired.

24:27.940 --> 24:29.490
As soon as they heard
Qi was arrested,

24:29.490 --> 24:31.550
all his underlings started to crack.

24:31.590 --> 24:32.390
It's natural.

24:32.680 --> 24:34.680
They were only afraid of their boss.

24:34.790 --> 24:36.640
Now one after another,

24:36.640 --> 24:37.720
they're all rushing to confess.

24:37.720 --> 24:38.780
Careful, it's hot.

24:40.070 --> 24:41.400
Did they mention Qi Yan?

24:42.510 --> 24:43.970
You hit the nail on the head.

24:43.970 --> 24:45.960
Whether he's Qi Yan or Old Scorpion,

24:45.960 --> 24:47.490
he's vanished into thin air.

24:47.490 --> 24:48.520
The regular underlings

24:48.520 --> 24:49.500
aren't high enough in the ranks

24:49.500 --> 24:51.500
to provide any useful information.

24:51.960 --> 24:54.200
Only Qi could get close to him.

24:54.440 --> 24:55.480
But this guy

24:55.590 --> 24:58.790
hasn't said a word
since he was brought in.

24:59.270 --> 25:01.070
The old fox is keeping his mouth shut.

25:01.070 --> 25:02.030
I'm thinking

25:02.240 --> 25:03.830
that if we want to find him,

25:04.070 --> 25:06.310
we need to try other approaches.

25:06.920 --> 25:08.070
Okay, got it.

25:08.630 --> 25:09.260
Good.

25:09.860 --> 25:10.790
I'll hang up now.

25:19.990 --> 25:20.910
Tell Mom for me

25:21.130 --> 25:23.730
that I finished all the soup.
It was delicious.

25:25.550 --> 25:26.550
Do you think Qi Yan

25:27.750 --> 25:30.150
will really disappear
for five or six years

25:30.440 --> 25:31.840
and then make a comeback?

25:33.480 --> 25:35.480
We still have a trump card up our sleeve.

25:35.480 --> 25:37.740
We're not afraid of him not reappearing.

25:38.310 --> 25:39.110
Qi Zhen?

25:40.350 --> 25:41.950
But will she help the police?

25:42.550 --> 25:44.080
Besides, Qi Yan is a madman.

25:44.790 --> 25:46.000
If we provoke him,

25:47.550 --> 25:49.310
more people could get hurt.

25:51.350 --> 25:53.010
Using Qi Zhen as our trump card

25:53.830 --> 25:55.350
to break down Qi Yan's
psychological defenses

25:55.350 --> 25:56.960
is the most effective approach

25:56.960 --> 25:58.220
but also the riskiest.

25:59.030 --> 26:01.430
We can't gamble with other people's lives.

26:01.720 --> 26:04.000
Then who is this trump card
you're talking about?

26:04.000 --> 26:04.920
Prof recently found

26:04.920 --> 26:07.200
a new witness in
the Huaiguang serial murder cases—

26:07.200 --> 26:08.260
Chen Li's ex-wife.

26:08.750 --> 26:10.310
Chen Li's ex-wife?

26:14.130 --> 26:15.060
Back then,

26:16.350 --> 26:18.480
I was the one who collected that money.

26:22.590 --> 26:23.200
Go on.

26:24.270 --> 26:26.130
Before Chen Li turned himself in,

26:26.440 --> 26:27.720
he came to see me.

26:30.110 --> 26:31.840
He was very emotional that day.

26:33.110 --> 26:35.830
He talked more than he ever did before.

26:36.860 --> 26:39.080
He said he was mediocre and incompetent,

26:39.080 --> 26:41.080
that he failed to be a good husband

26:41.510 --> 26:42.550
or a good father.

26:43.440 --> 26:44.350
Finally,

26:45.640 --> 26:47.110
he said over these years,

26:47.590 --> 26:49.520
he had secretly saved up some money

26:49.840 --> 26:52.800
and someone would deliver it
to our home in a few days.

26:53.850 --> 26:56.110
He told me that once I received the money,

26:56.750 --> 26:59.150
I should take our son
and leave the country.

26:59.600 --> 27:01.750
I was very surprised at the time.

27:03.960 --> 27:05.200
But at that time,

27:06.110 --> 27:07.570
we were already divorced.

27:08.270 --> 27:09.930
He wouldn't tell me anything,

27:10.250 --> 27:12.380
and I couldn't get much more out of him.

27:16.380 --> 27:18.060
How did you get this money?

27:19.070 --> 27:20.310
A few days later,

27:21.110 --> 27:22.310
a group of people

27:22.550 --> 27:23.750
came to our home.

27:24.960 --> 27:27.160
They said they were entrusted by Chen Li

27:28.070 --> 27:29.920
and gave me an offshore account.

27:32.880 --> 27:33.960
And some cash.

27:36.520 --> 27:38.300
Their leader

27:38.440 --> 27:39.920
was a young man,

27:40.720 --> 27:41.880
about 20 years old,

27:42.350 --> 27:43.510
wearing a suit.

27:44.240 --> 27:45.770
He looked like a gentleman.

27:46.360 --> 27:47.640
He didn't speak,

27:48.750 --> 27:50.110
but I could tell

27:50.480 --> 27:52.400
that the others, though older,

27:52.960 --> 27:54.400
all followed his lead.

27:54.920 --> 27:56.050
He didn't say a word?

27:58.570 --> 27:59.770
You're a good mother.

28:01.680 --> 28:03.050
For your son's sake,

28:04.120 --> 28:05.980
don't say anything unnecessary.

28:06.940 --> 28:08.020
After you leave,

28:09.510 --> 28:10.660
don't come back.

28:12.990 --> 28:13.840
Understand?

28:16.410 --> 28:17.810
That's all he said.

28:19.000 --> 28:20.110
Not long after that,

28:20.110 --> 28:21.270
I saw in the newspaper

28:21.270 --> 28:23.200
that Chen Li had turned himself in.

28:24.510 --> 28:26.040
Without thinking too much,

28:26.790 --> 28:29.190
I pretty much understood
what was going on.

28:30.070 --> 28:30.920
Later,

28:31.640 --> 28:33.350
Officer Wang, you came

28:33.350 --> 28:35.350
to ask me about Chen Li's situation.

28:36.110 --> 28:37.070
At that time,

28:37.590 --> 28:39.120
I didn't dare say a word more

28:39.620 --> 28:41.480
for fear of getting into trouble.

28:41.590 --> 28:43.720
After all, my son was still young then.

28:44.270 --> 28:45.730
Then why did you come back?

28:48.030 --> 28:49.830
Carrying a secret for too long

28:50.200 --> 28:51.330
doesn't lighten it.

28:52.430 --> 28:54.760
Instead, it becomes heavier and heavier.

28:56.830 --> 28:57.960
I came back this time

28:59.000 --> 29:01.680
to make some amends.

29:02.720 --> 29:03.640
I didn't expect

29:03.700 --> 29:05.660
you would find me so quickly.

29:10.510 --> 29:12.310
Did you show them Qi Yan's photo?

29:13.020 --> 29:13.510
Yes.

29:14.240 --> 29:15.770
They said it looks like him.

29:15.960 --> 29:16.910
But you think

29:17.710 --> 29:18.920
he was not Qi Yan,

29:19.240 --> 29:19.890
right?

29:22.680 --> 29:24.740
Qi Zhen's life was really difficult.

29:24.790 --> 29:26.240
If Qi Yan lived with her,

29:26.680 --> 29:28.330
he couldn't possibly have had
that much money.

29:28.330 --> 29:29.200
Even if he did,

29:29.750 --> 29:32.030
it would be impossible
to tie up all those loose ends

29:32.030 --> 29:33.550
to tie up all those loose ends.

29:33.550 --> 29:35.550
Qi Yan barely went to school as a kid,

29:35.680 --> 29:37.440
let alone arrange for someone
to take the blame,

29:37.440 --> 29:38.200
flee abroad,

29:38.290 --> 29:40.150
and eliminate all consequences.

29:40.640 --> 29:42.370
He couldn't have done it alone.

29:43.680 --> 29:44.940
To accomplish all this

29:45.440 --> 29:47.170
requires more than just money.

29:47.200 --> 29:48.510
It also takes
certain connections and power.

29:48.510 --> 29:49.160
So that means

29:49.160 --> 29:50.790
we can draw two conclusions.

29:51.110 --> 29:51.590
First,

29:52.440 --> 29:54.440
the person Chen Li's ex-wife met

29:55.130 --> 29:56.200
worked with Qi Yan.

29:56.520 --> 29:57.110
Second,

29:57.520 --> 29:58.250
this person,

29:58.310 --> 29:59.630
despite being young,

30:00.030 --> 30:01.750
had extensive social resources

30:01.750 --> 30:02.950
and powerful backing

30:02.960 --> 30:04.960
that shouldn't be underestimated.

30:08.930 --> 30:11.260
Do you remember what Yu Liang said before?

30:11.550 --> 30:13.270
That Qi Zhen always had hallucinations

30:13.270 --> 30:15.670
about someone trying to take her children?

30:17.350 --> 30:18.670
Perhaps Qi Zhen's hallucinations

30:18.670 --> 30:20.000
weren't just delusions

30:20.200 --> 30:21.530
but actually happened.

30:21.790 --> 30:23.650
Back then, she gave birth to twins

30:23.740 --> 30:25.340
and for some unknown reason,

30:25.400 --> 30:27.590
she left the children's biological father.

30:27.590 --> 30:30.160
After that, someone kept fighting her
for custody of the children.

30:30.160 --> 30:30.760
In the end,

30:31.170 --> 30:33.030
one child was taken by the father,

30:33.140 --> 30:33.950
while the other

30:33.950 --> 30:35.680
remained hidden with the mother.

30:35.680 --> 30:36.560
If we think about it this way,

30:36.560 --> 30:37.820
it all makes sense now.

30:38.330 --> 30:40.050
Indeed, no one has ever

30:40.440 --> 30:41.970
mentioned Qi Yan's father.

30:43.590 --> 30:45.480
Maybe he's the key to all this.

30:47.000 --> 30:48.130
Twenty years ago...

30:49.310 --> 30:52.310
Twenty years ago,
the twins had just entered society.

30:52.960 --> 30:53.890
He must be the one

30:54.400 --> 30:57.000
with enough power
to orchestrate everything.

30:57.160 --> 30:59.090
Qi Yan committed terrible crimes.

30:59.510 --> 31:01.590
This brother
who stayed with their biological father

31:01.590 --> 31:03.320
helped cover up all his crimes,

31:04.070 --> 31:04.990
including making Chen Li

31:04.990 --> 31:06.250
take the blame for him.

31:07.040 --> 31:09.000
After everything was taken care of,

31:09.000 --> 31:10.000
he brought Qi Yan

31:10.030 --> 31:11.890
back to their biological father.

31:12.190 --> 31:13.080
So Qi Yan

31:13.720 --> 31:15.380
also gained powerful backing

31:15.620 --> 31:17.350
and later became Old Scorpion.

31:18.030 --> 31:19.350
If we think about it this way,

31:19.350 --> 31:20.750
everything makes sense.

31:21.200 --> 31:22.310
What kind of person

31:23.920 --> 31:25.180
is this brother of his?

31:27.310 --> 31:29.030
He and Chen Li's ex-wife

31:29.200 --> 31:30.860
only exchanged one sentence.

31:31.440 --> 31:32.770
She said on the surface,

31:33.000 --> 31:34.530
he seemed like a gentleman.

31:35.440 --> 31:37.440
That's all the information we have.

31:40.400 --> 31:42.060
Jiang Cheng mentioned before

31:42.240 --> 31:43.640
that people around Qi Yan

31:44.750 --> 31:46.490
all called him Young Master Wen.

31:46.490 --> 31:47.420
Do you remember?

31:48.680 --> 31:49.680
Young Master Wen?

31:50.750 --> 31:53.000
I've never heard anyone else
call him Qi Yan.

31:53.000 --> 31:54.240
People close to him

31:54.260 --> 31:55.990
all call him Young Master Wen..

31:56.070 --> 31:57.590
It seems like some kind of honorific

31:57.590 --> 31:58.640
or a nickname.

31:59.450 --> 32:00.720
So in our minds,

32:01.060 --> 32:03.030
the Qi Yan in the warehouse
is already dead.

32:03.030 --> 32:04.130
But this Young Master Wen

32:04.130 --> 32:04.990
is still alive.

32:23.680 --> 32:25.010
Stop thinking about it.

32:25.070 --> 32:26.070
You're tired too.

32:27.480 --> 32:28.310
Get some rest.

32:29.750 --> 32:30.750
Brush your teeth,

32:31.070 --> 32:32.600
take a shower, and go to bed.

32:40.550 --> 32:41.410
Go to sleep now.

33:02.270 --> 33:03.900
We haven't slept together for days.

33:03.900 --> 33:05.770
Move over. Hurry up.

33:38.400 --> 33:39.400
Professor Jiang,

33:40.350 --> 33:42.750
the person you shot
and killed back then...

33:44.000 --> 33:44.830
Who was it?

33:46.720 --> 33:47.770
Of course I know.

33:48.510 --> 33:50.170
that you don't want to die now.

33:50.960 --> 33:52.270
You must be thinking

33:53.410 --> 33:54.920
that if you died now,

33:55.720 --> 33:58.450
what would happen
to the girl you care about most?

34:01.240 --> 34:02.640
What's wrong, Hansheng?

34:03.790 --> 34:05.120
Are you feeling unwell?

34:05.160 --> 34:05.960
It's nothing.

34:05.980 --> 34:07.380
Did you have a nightmare?

34:19.190 --> 34:20.449
After I'm discharged,

34:21.360 --> 34:22.360
I want to formally request

34:22.360 --> 34:24.090
an extended leave from school.

34:24.840 --> 34:25.920
For how long?

34:27.000 --> 34:28.070
A whole semester?

34:31.360 --> 34:32.960
Until Qi Yan is caught.

34:37.230 --> 34:38.830
If the school doesn't agree,

34:39.150 --> 34:40.440
I might have to resign.

34:41.670 --> 34:42.889
Will Professor Wang

34:43.510 --> 34:44.670
be upset?

34:45.510 --> 34:47.510
After all, he recommended you
to the position.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.400
No, he won't.

34:49.630 --> 34:50.960
He understands me best.

34:53.900 --> 34:55.250
Then I support you too.

34:56.870 --> 34:58.530
I understand you best as well.

35:19.320 --> 35:20.250
Jiang Hansheng.

35:23.030 --> 35:24.030
How did you always

35:25.360 --> 35:26.710
manage to find me?

35:28.190 --> 35:29.850
I installed a tracking system

35:30.190 --> 35:31.550
on your phone,

35:33.360 --> 35:34.400
and in your ring.

35:35.960 --> 35:37.440
That's going too far!

35:37.440 --> 35:38.070
I know.

35:39.230 --> 35:40.710
I know it wasn't right.

35:41.290 --> 35:41.930
I'm sorry.

35:43.030 --> 35:44.160
When did you do this?

35:46.150 --> 35:46.760
August.

35:49.550 --> 35:51.810
The day we visited your brother's grave,

35:52.400 --> 35:53.730
I found the pocket watch

35:53.750 --> 35:55.010
next to the tombstone.

35:56.710 --> 35:58.110
Them returning the watch

35:58.630 --> 36:00.690
was nothing but a declaration of war.

36:01.960 --> 36:03.560
I've dealt with them before.

36:04.030 --> 36:05.400
One slip-up

36:06.280 --> 36:08.590
could lead to irreversible consequences.

36:08.590 --> 36:10.190
So while you were showering,

36:11.630 --> 36:13.510
I messed with your phone

36:13.920 --> 36:14.840
and your ring.

36:17.880 --> 36:18.480
Hansheng.

36:20.890 --> 36:22.620
I'll freshen up. Won't be long.

36:23.510 --> 36:24.190
No rush.

36:46.710 --> 36:48.040
Can you keep wearing it?

36:48.670 --> 36:50.110
After we catch Qi Yan,

36:50.440 --> 36:52.100
you can take it off if you want.

36:56.590 --> 36:57.120
Alright.

36:57.990 --> 36:59.050
Let's do that then.

37:00.760 --> 37:01.760
I don't want you to

37:02.760 --> 37:04.090
worry too much about me.

37:05.360 --> 37:06.560
The ring doesn't also

37:07.280 --> 37:09.480
have listening capabilities, does it?

37:10.590 --> 37:11.720
I didn't go that far.

37:12.960 --> 37:13.590
Really?

37:17.920 --> 37:18.710
Fine.

37:29.280 --> 37:30.880
I hope we can catch

37:32.320 --> 37:33.780
Qi Yan before the New Year.

37:35.320 --> 37:35.800
We will.

37:44.560 --> 37:45.220
Good night.

37:47.760 --> 37:48.670
Good night.

38:46.800 --> 38:49.000
Neither of them like to smile in photos.

39:11.580 --> 39:12.140
Zhou Jin.

39:15.710 --> 39:16.440
How did it go?

39:17.510 --> 39:19.700
The Provincial Bureau leaders
coordinated everything.

39:19.700 --> 39:20.410
The school has agreed

39:20.410 --> 39:22.190
that I can prioritize
the investigation work.

39:22.190 --> 39:24.000
I'll be on temporary assignment
for one semester first,

39:24.000 --> 39:25.710
and we'll see how it goes.

39:26.000 --> 39:27.150
That's pretty good.

39:29.400 --> 39:30.420
Let's go check out my office.

39:30.420 --> 39:31.050
Let's go.

39:34.840 --> 39:36.040
The photo looks nice.

39:37.400 --> 39:39.460
Not as good as the real person though.

40:05.920 --> 40:06.920
Professor Jiang,

40:07.000 --> 40:08.660
can I borrow a couple of books?

40:10.000 --> 40:12.000
I'll bring them
all to your place sometime.

40:12.000 --> 40:13.320
That's not necessary.

40:13.510 --> 40:14.630
I'm a slow reader.

40:15.440 --> 40:16.700
Just lend me two books,

40:17.230 --> 40:19.230
that preferably aren't too boring.

40:23.480 --> 40:25.150
This one is about psychoanalysis.

40:25.150 --> 40:26.110
It's about women.

40:26.110 --> 40:27.110
You might like it.

40:36.440 --> 40:37.170
And this one.

40:38.110 --> 40:38.920
I like it.

40:44.680 --> 40:45.660
In Cold Blood.

40:49.070 --> 40:50.060
It's a a crime investigation book

40:50.060 --> 40:51.270
that blends fiction

40:52.110 --> 40:53.070
with factual record.

40:53.070 --> 40:54.600
It even has a film adaption.

40:55.150 --> 40:56.230
Why do you like it?

41:00.320 --> 41:01.070
Everyone might have

41:01.070 --> 41:02.670
grown up in a small dark room.

41:03.440 --> 41:05.840
Some choose to walk out
through the front door,

41:05.840 --> 41:07.440
and others through the back.

41:08.760 --> 41:10.670
They all should deserve sympathy,

41:10.670 --> 41:12.480
but because of their different exits,

41:12.480 --> 41:13.230
good and evil

41:13.350 --> 41:14.750
become clearly defined.

41:16.330 --> 41:17.730
Human nature is complex.

41:18.190 --> 41:20.190
I like this book's self-reflection

41:20.320 --> 41:21.250
and compassion.

41:24.950 --> 41:26.280
I'll read it carefully.

41:32.320 --> 41:33.120
Is class over?

41:34.110 --> 41:34.970
Yes, it's over.

41:39.360 --> 41:40.490
It's already 11:50.

41:42.030 --> 41:42.760
What's this?

41:44.320 --> 41:45.400
It's an old video

41:46.230 --> 41:47.480
of my brother.

41:47.840 --> 41:48.640
You can watch.

41:53.760 --> 41:55.360
This was their competition.

41:55.480 --> 41:57.010
My brother won first place.

41:57.190 --> 41:58.520
When was this recorded?

41:59.550 --> 42:00.750
This was my brother's

42:01.960 --> 42:03.510
last recorded video.

42:04.590 --> 42:05.650
It's an interview.

42:06.350 --> 42:07.040
It's recording.

42:07.040 --> 42:07.700
Recording.

42:07.800 --> 42:09.550
Next on camera is

42:09.550 --> 42:11.550
the former Deputy Captain
of the Cheetah Strike Force,

42:11.550 --> 42:13.190
the champion of
the 13th Sniper Shooting Individual Event.

42:13.190 --> 42:14.110
Is that Zhao Ping?

42:14.110 --> 42:15.280
The best competitor

42:15.630 --> 42:17.670
and candidate
for Deputy Chief of the Special Police.

42:17.670 --> 42:18.760
This is too blurry.

42:18.780 --> 42:19.910
I can't see clearly.

42:19.960 --> 42:21.160
The pride of our unit,

42:21.370 --> 42:22.730
Captain Zhou Chuan!

42:22.960 --> 42:23.560
Applause!

42:23.760 --> 42:24.400
Hooray!

42:36.860 --> 42:38.390
It does look like Zhao Ping.

42:38.920 --> 42:40.840
Although the video is a bit blurry,

42:40.840 --> 42:42.900
a person's posture is hard to change.

42:43.320 --> 42:45.320
Zhao Ping usually hunches his back,

42:45.710 --> 42:46.760
with his left side

42:47.230 --> 42:48.590
slightly lower than the right.

42:48.590 --> 42:49.840
He also has uneven shoulders.

42:49.840 --> 42:50.360
I see.

42:51.960 --> 42:52.820
Hello, Senior.

42:53.590 --> 42:55.190
It really does seem to be him.

42:55.280 --> 42:56.810
But that's not surprising.

42:56.960 --> 42:57.920
He and my brother

42:58.320 --> 42:59.520
were in the same unit.

43:05.480 --> 43:06.590
Who's that person next to him?
